[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0087","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0087.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0103","title":"SmartCart 购物车应用 隐藏表单字段篡改漏洞","description":"SmartCart 购物车应用程序存在隐藏表单字段篡改漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过篡改 HTML 表单中的隐藏字段（如商品价格、数量、商品 ID 等敏感购买参数），绕过客户端验证直接提交篡改后的订单数据，导致以极低价格甚至零价格购买商品、修改订单金额或篡改其他敏感交易信息。该漏洞源于服务端未对提交的表单数据进行完整性校验与服务端价格校验，影响所有部署 SmartCart 购物车系统的电商站点，攻击者无需认证即可通过浏览器开发者工具或代理工具篡改表单提交实施攻击，CVSS 2.0 评分 7.5，属高危漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0103"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:00.427","remediation":"不要在 HTML 隐藏表单字段中存放商品价格、数量、金额等敏感交易数据，改为在服务端会话或数据库中维护权威价格与库存信息；订单提交时以服务端商品 ID 重新查询价格并进行二次校验，拒绝客户端传入的价格与金额字段；对所有表单参数做完整性校验（如加签名/HMAC 校验），并记录异常订单以便审计。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0103","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0103.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0103","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/a833b276bb98d0827a91a3688fb32766b685cf2a/2000/CVE-2000-0103.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0103.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gh9x-4gjw-xqw7/GHSA-gh9x-4gjw-xqw7.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0103.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88331/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/47100ba13b280d8b2c20065cb4252225c6015d54/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0087.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0086","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0086.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0102","title":"SalesCart 购物车应用程序表单字段篡改漏洞","description":"SalesCart 是一款基于 Web 的购物车应用程序，其存在敏感数据可被篡改的安全漏洞。该应用的购买流程依赖前端 HTML 表单中的隐藏字段（hidden form fields）来传递商品价格、数量等关键信息，但服务端未对这些字段进行真实性校验与重新计算。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过拦截并修改提交订单时的隐藏表单字段（如商品单价、总价），将金额篡改为任意数值后提交，从而以极低价格完成购买。该漏洞影响所有使用 SalesCart 购物车且未在服务端校验订单数据的站点，攻击仅需能够访问目标购物页面并发起 HTTP 请求即可，利用门槛低，可直接造成商家经济损失。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0102"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:00.290","remediation":"立即升级 SalesCart 至官方已修复版本（1.5 及以上），并在服务端对订单金额、商品数量等敏感字段进行二次校验与签名防篡改，禁止信任客户端提交的隐藏表单值；如暂无法升级，应在服务端移除对隐藏字段的依赖、改用会话存储订单状态作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0102","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0102.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0102.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0102","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/a833b276bb98d0827a91a3688fb32766b685cf2a/2000/CVE-2000-0102.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Glanz/CVE-2000-0102.xml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0102.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m6p3-p77r-m43h/GHSA-m6p3-p77r-m43h.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0102.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88348/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0086.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0086.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0085","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0085.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0101","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9116,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10802}}","description":"Make-a-Store OrderPage 购物车应用程序存在信息修改漏洞，该应用在处理订单时使用隐藏表单字段传递敏感购买信息（如商品价格、数量、用户标识等），但未对客户端提交的数据进行严格的服务端校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过拦截或篡改页面中的隐藏表单字段，将敏感购买信息修改为任意值，从而以更低价格完成订单或篡改购买内容。该漏洞影响部署 Make-a-Store OrderPage 购物车应用的网站，攻击者只需通过浏览器开发者工具或代理工具修改隐藏字段参数即可发起利用，无需复杂技术手段，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0101"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:00.167","remediation":"立即升级 Make-a-Store OrderPage 至官方修复版本（2000 年 2 月及之后的安全发布版），并在服务器端对订单金额、数量、商品 ID 等敏感字段做重算与签名校验，丢弃前端提交的隐藏表单值；部署前用 WAF 规则拦截篡改 price/total 等隐藏字段的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0101","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0101.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2d7ee098b36909e6f1960d9a77b8043812c482f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0101.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0101","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/871c5513ef49462cb040dfc7b547cbae28b6ad6b/2000/CVE-2000-0101.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0101.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0101.json","https://github.com/feststelltaste/software-analytics/blob/e0a9cb3397bfdc5537f1d13415fb6ffdca1ce6d9/prototypes/CVE%20Analysis.ipynb","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-472.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0085.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0085.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0400","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0400.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0133","title":"H. Nomura Tiny FTPDaemon 0.52 多缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Tiny FTPd 0.52 beta3 FTP服务器在处理STOR、RNTO、MKD、XMKD、RMD、XRMD、APPE、SIZE和RNFR等命令时存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的长参数触发溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意代码，完全控制受影响服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0133"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-01","updated":"2000-02-01","remediation":"该软件已停止维护，建议立即停止使用Tiny FTPd 0.52 beta3，迁移至其他受支持的FTP服务器软件如FileZilla Server或vsftpd，并确保系统防火墙限制FTP服务的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T02:41:44.264234904+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/961"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0400.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0112","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0123","title":"FileMaker 购物车应用 隐藏表单字段 购买信息篡改漏洞","description":"FileMaker Pro 附带的购物车示例程序在处理订单时信任客户端提交的隐藏表单字段，攻击者可通过修改这些字段（如订单金额、商品数量、收货地址等）远程篡改敏感的购买信息。该漏洞无需身份认证即可通过网络远程利用，破坏交易数据的完整性与机密性，可能导致商家经济损失或用户隐私泄露。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0123"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-01","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级到 FileMaker Pro 5.0v3 或更高版本，并替换官方购物车示例程序为企业定制版本。在服务端对订单金额、数量等关键字段进行二次校验与重算，不信任客户端提交的值。移除所有隐藏表单字段，采用会话机制在服务端保存购物车状态，并启用 HTTPS 加密传输防止中间人篡改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0123","https://www.ibm.com/security/xforce/vulnerabilities/3067","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0123.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0112.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0093","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0108","title":"Intellivend 在线购物车隐藏表单字段敏感信息篡改漏洞","description":"Intellivend 在线购物车应用程序存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过修改 HTML 隐藏表单字段来篡改价格、数量等敏感购买信息。由于应用程序在服务端未对客户端提交的参数进行重新校验，攻击者可以通过浏览器代理工具拦截并修改表单中的隐藏字段值，将商品价格修改为极低数值或更改购买数量，从而以远低于正常价格的价格完成购买交易。此漏洞不需要任何认证即可利用，任何网络可达的攻击者均可发起攻击，导致商家遭受经济损失。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0108"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"由于 Intellivend 官方未发布正式补丁，根本修复措施为：将所有价格、数量等敏感购买信息从 HTML 隐藏表单字段移至服务端会话（Session）中存储，在服务端对每次购买请求中的价格和数量进行重新计算与校验，不得信任客户端提交的隐藏字段值。购物车应使用服务端生成的唯一标识符关联商品条目，而非依赖客户端传入的商品 ID 或价格参数。建议部署 WAF 规则对包含价格、金额参数的请求进行异常检测与拦截。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0108","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0108.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gvqh-48v6-r4xm/GHSA-gvqh-48v6-r4xm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88314/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0093.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0090","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0105","title":"Microsoft Outlook Express 5 JavaScript 邮件访问漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Express 5 存在 JavaScript 变量访问漏洞，攻击者可通过访问引用后续已读邮件的脚本变量，远程查看用户邮箱中的邮件内容。此漏洞导致未授权访问用户电子邮件隐私信息，影响用户数据安全。攻击者无需身份验证即可利用此漏洞获取邮箱中的邮件内容。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0105"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-01","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"建议升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 1 或更高版本（含修复补丁 KB247962），或升级至 Outlook Express 6.0/Windows Live Mail 等更新版本。临时缓解措施：在 IE“Internet 选项 → 安全 → 受限站点”区域将“活动脚本”设为“禁用”，并在 Outlook Express“工具 → 选项 → 安全”选项卡勾选“限制站点区域”，禁止 HTML 邮件运行脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/962","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0105.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0105.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0308","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0308.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0109","title":"Standard & Poors ComStock MultiCSP 默认账户与空口令漏洞","description":"Standard & Poors ComStock 金融数据服务中的 MultiCSP（mcsp Client Site Processor）系统在安装时创建了多个默认账户，这些账户要么没有设置密码，要么使用了极易猜测的默认密码。远程攻击者可利用这些弱口令账户登录系统，获取完全控制权限，导致机密性、完整性和可用性全面受损。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0109"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"删除或禁用所有默认账户，为必要账户设置强密码策略，限制系统管理接口的网络访问范围，仅允许受信任 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T01:13:41.785482847+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0109","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0109"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0308.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0308.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0308.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0119","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0119.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0132","title":"Microsoft Java Virtual Machine getSystemResourceAsStream 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Java Virtual Machine（JVM）中存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送恶意 Java Applet，利用 getSystemResourceAsStream() 函数读取本地文件系统中的敏感文件。攻击者需知道文件名且文件必须位于 JVM 主目录或 CLASSPATH 环境变量指定路径中。该漏洞可导致系统敏感信息（如 AUTOEXEC.BAT 等配置文件）被未授权读取。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0132"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"微软已发布安全公告 MS00-005 提供补丁修复此漏洞。用户应通过 Windows Update 安装补丁，或升级到包含修复的最新版本 Internet Explorer（4.01 SP2 及以上版本）。对于无法安装补丁的系统，建议禁用 Java Applet 执行功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/957","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19734","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0132"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19734"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0119.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0119.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0119.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0102","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0117","title":"Cobalt RaQ2 siteUserMod.cgi 认证绕过权限提升漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器固件 2.0.15 及更早版本中，内置的 siteUserMod.cgi 程序未对请求来源和身份进行充分校验，远程攻击者无需提供管理员凭据即可直接向该 CGI 接口发送特制请求，绕过正常认证流程并修改站点用户参数、添加或提升用户权限，从而获取服务器管理控制权。攻击者可利用该漏洞在无需本地访问的情况下，通过网络对暴露的 RaQ2 管理 Web 服务发起请求完成提权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0117"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-30","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 Cobalt RaQ2 服务器固件至 2.0.16 及以上版本（Sun Cobalt 官方已发布修复补丁），或升级至 RaQ3/4 系列设备。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器配置中限制 /cgi-bin/siteUserMod.cgi 仅允许受信任管理员 IP 访问，或通过 .htaccess 添加访问限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/951","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0117.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w7xc-wpq5-5vgr/GHSA-w7xc-wpq5-5vgr.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/siteUserMod.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0102.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0101","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0116","title":"Check Point Firewall-1 脚本标签检查绕过漏洞","description":"Check Point Software Firewall-1 3.0 存在脚本标签过滤绕过漏洞。该防火墙未能正确过滤 HTML 中的 script 标签，远程攻击者可通过在 SCRIPT 标签前额外添加一个 \"<\" 字符来绕过 \"Strip Script Tags\" 安全限制，导致恶意脚本代码可被注入并执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞，影响 Check Point Firewall-1 3.0 版本。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0116"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:02.023","remediation":"升级到 Check Point 官方已修复此问题的后续版本（Firewall-1 4.0 及以上），或迁移至当前受支持的 Check Point Quantum 系列防火墙。在 Security Server 的 HTTP Security Server 配置中启用严格标签过滤规则，并禁用不安全的 HTTP 协议解析选项。对于无法立即升级的环境，可在网络边界部署 WAF 或反向代理，对请求中的 `<script` 和 `<<script` 等变体进行正则过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1212","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/954","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19732","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0116.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0116","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0116.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0116.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhf9-r8ff-33pc/GHSA-vhf9-r8ff-33pc.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_500_600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0116.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-167.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001123.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--29222771-9a98-489f-8f34-1fde553f4c76.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0101.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0101.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0095","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0095.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0111","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9112,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10796}}","description":"RightFax Web 客户端在会话管理中使用可预测的会话标识数字，而非随机不可猜测的令牌。远程攻击者可在未认证情况下，通过观察会话编号的生成规律预测其他用户的合法会话 ID，从而劫持已登录用户的会话并冒充其身份访问系统。该漏洞影响部署了 RightFax Web 客户端的产品，攻击者只需能访问目标 Web 服务并获取会话标识即可发起劫持，无需本地权限或用户交互，可被用于越权访问敏感传真数据及后台功能。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0111"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:01.420","remediation":"建议升级到 RightFax 12.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了会话数字预测漏洞并实现了随机会话 ID 生成。如无法立即升级，可通过修改 web 客户端配置文件，禁用默认的 session.inc.php 文件并启用会话加盐和过期机制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/953","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0111.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0111","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0111.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0111.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xpxq-j6pj-5vxg/GHSA-xpxq-j6pj-5vxg.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0111.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001122.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fd4916152066cf69446b0fbd8f7bb3a97a137e13/2000.tsv","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0095.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0117","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0117.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0130","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10432,\"inputTokens\":337,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10788}}","description":"SCO UnixWare 中的 scohelp 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的恶意请求触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以 scohelp 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 7.x 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危），攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过发送超长参数导致栈缓冲区溢出劫持控制流，进而执行任意 Shell 命令获取系统控制权。SCO 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议尽快升级至修复版本或禁用 scohelp 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0130"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:03.790","remediation":"立即应用 SCO UnixWare 7.1.4 或更高版本的安全补丁包 (SP4+)，其中修复了 scohelp 程序的缓冲区溢出问题，或启用内核地址空间布局随机化 (KASLR) 和数据执行保护 (DEP) 以缓解该漏洞。如无法立即更新，建议在 /etc/services 文件中删除或重命名 scohelp 服务以禁用该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94908470928258&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0130.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0130","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0130.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0130.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-pqq3-v6fg-mvw9/GHSA-pqq3-v6fg-mvw9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83023/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0130.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/db2259ea67d1f5e8ce454c4a2cee60d344017bd3/2000.tsv","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/b7580d6aba8040c22f37d85dec61d19c97d13189/advisories/2022/05/EUVD-2000-0129.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0117.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0097","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0113","title":"SyGate 远程管理服务 访问控制缺陷导致拒绝服务与信息泄露漏洞","description":"SyGate 远程管理程序对其管理服务的访问权限控制存在缺陷，未能正确限制未授权访问。远程攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，可向目标系统发送特制请求连接该管理服务，从而触发拒绝服务（DoS）导致服务不可用，或非法获取网络流量统计数据等敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行 SyGate 远程管理服务的系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够与目标的管理服务端口建立网络连接。利用方式是通过网络发送恶意请求，造成服务瘫痪或信息泄露。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0113"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:01.660","remediation":"升级 SyGate 至官方发布的最新修复版本（4.0 及以上），并在 SyGate 远程管理服务中启用访问控制与强口令认证，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 访问管理端口（默认 TCP 1694）。如暂无法升级，可在边界防火墙或路由器上屏蔽该管理端口的外部连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94934808714972&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94952641025328&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94973281714994&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/952","http://www.sybergen.com/support/fix.htm","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5b55afba6f3a87fe9319e1de76170e4c2760d614/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0113.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0113","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0113.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0113.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj7c-7233-qrq9/GHSA-cj7c-7233-qrq9.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/sygate_remote_control.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0113.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bb58ccc3-e01d-425f-8257-bcd5c86c101f.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001120.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0082","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0082.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0098","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16278,\"outputTokens\":29,\"totalTokens\":16307}}","description":"Microsoft Index Server（索引服务器）的 Internet Data Query（.ida）处理机制存在信息泄漏缺陷。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标 Web 服务器发起一个针对不存在的 .ida 文件的 HTTP 请求，服务器便会返回包含该 Web 目录真实物理路径的错误信息。攻击者可借此探查服务器文件系统结构，为后续攻击收集路径情报。该漏洞影响运行 Microsoft Index Server 的 IIS Web 服务器，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标且存在 .ida 查询处理，利用方式简单，可通过常规 HTTP 请求触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0098"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:59.800","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Index Server 2.0 安装 Windows 2000 Service Pack 1 或更高版本补丁；在 IIS 中删除或限制对 .ida/.idq 文件的访问权限，并在防火墙/代理层屏蔽对 Internet Data Query 文件的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-006","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0098.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0098.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0098","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0098.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0098.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6jm-fjc7-97gj/GHSA-q6jm-fjc7-97gj.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0098.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_anything_idq.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001118.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0082.toml"}]